    "description": "<strong>Claritas</strong> 是一款2D回合制派对构建地下城爬行RPG，具有多种独特系统和机制。<br><br><strong>Claritas</strong> 提供多个可玩角色，每个角色都有四种独特的能力，允许无尽的战略组合。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从多样化的角色名单中构建你的队伍，能够在游戏过程中随时更换成员。</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用每次升级获得的技能点增强你的英雄能力。你可以随时自由重新分配这些点数，允许灵活的自定义。</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/66ef81d67bdecde76dc4b56fa55bc351.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/66ef81d67bdecde76dc4b56fa55bc351.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/66ef81d67bdecde76dc4b56fa55bc351.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接受赏金猎人的合同，消灭特定的怪物，获得经验值、金币和其他奖励。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/cef6a016c57932c08ee95e28180436e4.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/cef6a016c57932c08ee95e28180436e4.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/cef6a016c57932c08ee95e28180436e4.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁强大的特权，为你的整个队伍提供永久增强。</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/f2922b05961d87b117620882a8e11342.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/f2922b05961d87b117620882a8e11342.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地下城中遇到不可预测的随机事件，每个事件提供独特的选择，导致不同的结果。</p></li></ul>",
